---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sunglasses in Tijuana | UV Protection | Ópticas Jarmar Zona Río"
  description="Sunglasses with full UV protection in Tijuana. Prescription or non-prescription, wide style selection. Ópticas Jarmar Zona Río."
  alternates={[
    { hreflang: "en", href: "https://jarmar.com/en/tijuana/sunglasses/" },
    { hreflang: "es", href: "https://jarmar.com/tijuana/lentes-de-sol/" },
    { hreflang: "x-default", href: "https://jarmar.com/tijuana/lentes-de-sol/" }
  ]}
>
  <style>
    :root { --bg: #071A3E; --surface: #0D2B6B; --accent: #3A8FE0; }

    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, #1a4a8a 100%); color: #fff; padding: 100px 20px 80px; text-align: center; }
    .hero-tag { display: inline-block; background: rgba(58,143,224,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent); border-radius: 100px; padding: 6px 18px; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.85; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .btn-cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
    .btn-cta:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-2px); }

    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    .section { padding: 72px 20px; }
    .section:nth-child(even) { background: #f7f9fc; }
    .section-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section-title span { color: var(--accent); }
    .section-sub { color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 36px; }

    .uv-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .uv-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 18px; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58,143,224,0.2); padding: 28px 22px; text-align: center; }
    .uv-icon { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 14px; display: block; }
    .uv-card h4 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .uv-card p { color: #4a5568; font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    .tipos { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
    .tipo { background: var(--surface); color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px 20px; }
    .tipo h4 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .tipo p { font-size: 0.93rem; opacity: 0.85; line-height: 1.6; }

    .graduados-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%); border-radius: 24px; color: #fff; padding: 44px 40px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px; align-items: center; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .graduados-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .graduados-box h3 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .graduados-box p { font-size: 1.05rem; opacity: 0.85; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .check-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .check-list li { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 0.97rem; opacity: 0.9; }
    .check-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }

    .cta-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%); color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 80px 20px; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; opacity: 0.85; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 560px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

    .back-link { display: block; text-align: center; padding: 28px; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-tag">UV Protection · Tijuana</span>
      <h1>Sunglasses<br>in <span>Tijuana</span></h1>
      <p>Full UV protection, style, and quality in one piece. Tijuana's sunny climate demands real sunglasses. Available prescription or non-prescription.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+information+about+sunglasses+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        View collection →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why does <span>UV protection</span> matter?</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Not all sunglasses protect equally. Ultraviolet radiation can cause serious eye damage if your lenses lack certified UV protection.</p>
      <div class="uv-grid">
        <div class="uv-card">
          <span class="uv-icon">🌞</span>
          <h4>Premature cataracts</h4>
          <p>Chronic unprotected sun exposure accelerates cataract formation years earlier than expected.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="uv-card">
          <span class="uv-icon">👁️</span>
          <h4>Macular degeneration</h4>
          <p>UV rays contribute to damage of the macula, the area of the retina responsible for central vision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="uv-card">
          <span class="uv-icon">🔴</span>
          <h4>Pterygium & pinguecula</h4>
          <p>Benign growths on the eye surface caused by sun and wind exposure without protection.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Types of <span>sunglasses</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">We have the perfect option for every activity and lifestyle in Tijuana.</p>
      <div class="tipos">
        <div class="tipo">
          <h4>☀️ Polarized</h4>
          <p>Eliminate glare from water and asphalt. Ideal for driving and outdoor activities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tipo">
          <h4>🌊 Mirrored</h4>
          <p>Reflective exterior coat that reduces light entry. Great for high-brightness environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tipo">
          <h4>🎨 Photochromic</h4>
          <p>Darken in sunlight and clear indoors. Total versatility in one lens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tipo">
          <h4>🏃 Sports</h4>
          <p>Secure frames and impact-resistant lenses for physical activities and extreme sports.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Sunglasses <span>with prescription</span></h2>
      <div class="graduados-box">
        <div>
          <h3>See clearly and protect yourself from the sun — at the same time</h3>
          <p>You no longer have to choose between seeing well and being protected. We make your sunglasses with your exact prescription.</p>
          <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+information+about+prescription+sunglasses+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">Ask about options</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>Single vision prescription with solar filter</li>
          <li>Progressives with sun darkening</li>
          <li>Photochromic for indoor and outdoor use</li>
          <li>Available in polycarbonate and organic</li>
          <li>Certified UV400 protection</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Find your sunglasses in Tijuana</h2>
      <p>Visit us at Ópticas Jarmar Zona Río and discover our selection of sunglasses with real UV protection.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+information+about+sunglasses+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Book via WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a href="/en/tijuana/" class="back-link">← Back to Tijuana</a>
</BaseLayout>
